The PUBLISH_REQUESTED, DUE_FOR_DELETION tags are removed too. This RPC throws an exception if the version being archived is DRAFT, and if the `locked_by` user is not the same as the user performing the Archive. Audit fields updated include last_modified_timestamp, last_modified_by. Any existing lock is released when Archiving a integration. Currently, there is no unarchive mechanism.
